"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He inspired a generation of young swimmers and divers after winning a bronze medal in the individual 10m platform event at his home games at London 2012 when he was still a teenager.\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999631747876, \"rank\": 3.6824826928451215e-08, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a generation\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"young swimmers\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"divers\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual 10m platform event\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1182}, {\"ngram\": \"his home games\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley also clinched a memorable gold medal at the Tokyo 2020 Games, which took place in 2021 without any fans, and celebrated his final hurrah in Paris with silver.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994126938, \"rank\": 5.872883310704527e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"a memorable gold medal\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo 2020 Games\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"any fans\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"his final hurrah\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In total, he collected five Olympic medals.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"five Olympic medals\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beijing 2008Makes Olympics debut with Team GB at the age of 14 London 2012Wins bronze in the individual 10m platform event Rio 2016Claims bronze in the individual 10m platform event Tokyo 2020Wins first and only gold in synchronised 10m platform, becoming first British driver to win four Olympic medals Paris 2024Takes silver medal with Noah Williams in 10m synchronised platform competition In Paris, Daley's husband Dustin Lance Black and their two children, Robbie and Phoenix, watched on as he brought home a fifth medal.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.99999999954548, \"rank\": 3.155514787697194e-10, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1523, \"end\": 1529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999988228071396, \"rank\": 1.1652942339701e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1584, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999997981003821, \"rank\": 2.0189968105638757e-07, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1644, \"end\": 1649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"